snippet.title: 007 Racing PSX PS1 2000
snippet.description:
Gameplay of the Racing shooter game 007 Racing. This is another Playstation exclusive game by Eletronic Arts.

This game was dumped on by the gaming magazines at release for being well... just boring.

Once again they got a voice double for Pierce.
